DESCRIPTION:In this edition of Make @ MAP\, we invite you to slow down and reflect on the year that has passed. What made you smile\, think\, or feel proud? Create a self-portrait filled with the people\, places\, and moments that stood out for you this year.\n\nMake @ MAP is a series that allows you to explore our collection in an engaging and hands-on manner. These sessions allow you to create and take home a special souvenir of your visit. It is perfect for all ages — so bring your friends and family and get ready to make some art! No experience is necessary\, just a willingness to have fun and experiment with new materials.
